Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但橄榄石能从哪\N{\fnArial\fs48}But where could Peridot
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}传送这么强的信号？\N{\fnArial\fs48}be broadcasting a signal that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.34,0:01:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}只有一个地方\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's only one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.76,0:01:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}狮子，你还好吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Lion, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}正如我所担心的\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's as I feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看来橄榄石通过某些手段修复了通讯中枢站\N{\fnArial\fs48}It looks like Peridot somehow repaired the communication hub.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}或者，至少也是一部分\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, at least {\i1}some{\i} of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所以...我们只需要再一次砸坏它，对吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}So we just got to wreck it up again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们得融合成苏纪石\N{\fnArial\fs48}You guys should form Sugilite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}...是吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，我觉得，这得看石榴\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, uh, it's up to Garnet, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你怎么看？我们要不砸个爽？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What do you say? Shall we mash it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不\N{\fnArial\fs48}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但...难道我们不需要像上次一样巨大吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}But...Don't we need to be huge like last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}上次是场灾难\N{\fnArial\fs48}Last time was a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}上次我们融合时，苏纪石暴走了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Last time we fused, Sugilite went berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且归功于她我们之后都没法传送到这了\N{\fnArial\fs48}And it's because of her that we can't even warp here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我会变得草率，你则会变得鲁莽\N{\fnArial\fs48}I could be rash, you could be reckless,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}最后我们都会忘乎所以\N{\fnArial\fs48}and we could both get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所以，这次，苏纪石要下场了\N{\fnArial\fs48}So, for the time being, Sugilite is benched.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们现在需要的是仔细\N{\fnArial\fs48}What we need now is to be careful.
