Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}在即将彻底报废的通讯中枢为你现场直播\N{\fnArial\fs48}from the soon-to-be former communication hub.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们今晚怎么样？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How are y'all doing tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好极了\N{\fnArial\fs48} Great.
