Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢，我的星星啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, my stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这不是史蒂文·宇宙吗\N{\fnArial\fs48}If it isn't Steven Universe.
