Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么...你认为呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}So... What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等待我值吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Was I worth the wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我在说什么瞎话啊？当然啦\N{\fnArial\fs48}What am I saying? Of course I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔，你真能说会道啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wow. You're so articulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你不也是最可爱的小帅哥吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, aren't you the sweetest little charmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我现在真想将你在手心挤挤\N{\fnArial\fs48}I could literally squish you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}反正又不难\N{\fnArial\fs48}It would not be hard.
