Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对不起，我实在是太高兴我能来这里了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sorry. I'm just so excited to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你知道，我最近一直不能做自己呢\N{\fnArial\fs48}You see, I haven't exactly been myself lately.
