Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一旦你有求于可爱的红玛瑙，\N{\fnArial\fs48}If you ever have need of the lovely sardonyx,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}要告诉珍珠和石榴哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}let Pearl and Garnet know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我立刻就会出现-真的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll be there in a flash -- literally.
