Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们太棒了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You guys were amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们刚才真是这样？哦，那很好啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}We were? Oh. Well, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们赞爆了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}We were awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们为什么不经常这么做？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why don't we do that more often?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么，梨？为什么要对我撒谎？\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Why, pear?{\i} {\i1}Why did you lie to me?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不是故意的\N{\fnArial\fs48} {\i1}I didn't mean to.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢，梨\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aw. Pear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我会原谅她。你呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'd forgive her. Wouldn't you?
