Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔，嘿，紫晶\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, hey, Amethyst.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你要错过“哭泣早餐朋友”了\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're missing "crying breakfast friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我很好\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但这集目前为止非常好看\N{\fnArial\fs48}But it's a really good one so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}并不\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}别担心，我在录制，可以待会看\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't worry. I'm recording it for later.
