Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们得回去\N{\fnArial\fs48}We need to get back out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:05:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好\N{\fnArial\fs48} Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，狮子呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, where's Lion?
