Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你知道的\N{\fnArial\fs48}You know I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是什么？返场表演吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's this -- an encore performance?
