Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橄榄石已经回来过两次了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot's been back here twice,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}显然她还会再来第三次，对吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}so the odds are good she'll come back again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}Bam！这样我们就能抓到她了。\N{\fnArial\fs48}Bam! That's when we'll get her.
