Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}然后她会觉得我酷回来了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}And then she'll think I'm cool again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没有...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还是没有...\N{\fnArial\fs48}More nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！她在那！\N{\fnArial\fs48} There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，等等，那只是个奇怪的仙人掌\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, wait. That's just a weird cactus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我觉得她不会来了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't think she's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...你在干嘛？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, what are you doing?
