Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我感觉看到了什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}I think I saw something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是橄榄石的逃生舱\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's Peridot's escape pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她修好了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}She fixed it somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我还以为在我们手里\N{\fnArial\fs48}But I thought {\i1}we{\i} had it.
