Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦！\N{\fnArial\fs48} Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这可不好\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有什么不对吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}W-what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是橄榄石\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's Peridot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她肯定又修复了通讯中枢\N{\fnArial\fs48}She must have fixed the communication hub again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}通讯中枢又出事了\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's the hub again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她躲过了我的预知能力\N{\fnArial\fs48}She's evading my future vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不管试多少次，我都没法看见我们抓到橄榄石\N{\fnArial\fs48}No matter how many times I try, I can't see us finding Peridot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}快点，各位\N{\fnArial\fs48} Come on, team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不敢相信橄榄石带给我们这么多麻烦\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can't believe Peridot is giving us so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但这不算什么，对吗，石榴？\N{\fnArial\fs48}But it hardly matters, right, Garnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们能破坏这座塔\N{\fnArial\fs48}We can disable this tower
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不管要多少次，只要我们一起，对吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}as many times as we need to together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧。我准备好了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay. I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,130)}你准备好了吗，石榴？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Are you ready, Garnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我知道她在做什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know what she's doing. You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}停下！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有什么不对劲吗，紫晶？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is something the matter, Amethyst?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你-你不该这样\N{\fnArial\fs48}You -- you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠，我们看到你了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl, we saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你得告诉石榴是你\N{\fnArial\fs48}You need to tell Garnet it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一脸蒙b\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对不起\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这...只是...跟你一起成为红玛瑙真的很有趣\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's just so much fun being sardonyx with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}怪不得我看不到我们找到橄榄石\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's why I couldn't see us finding Peridot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等，听我解释\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait. Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是你一直在修复通讯中枢！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You've been fixing the hub!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真的是橄榄石...\N{\fnArial\fs48}It really {\i1}was{\i} Peridot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}第一次时\N{\fnArial\fs48}The first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:09:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你骗了我\N{\fnArial\fs48}You tricked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，不不不不，\N{\fnArial\fs48}No. No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，我们只是需要个融合的理由\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, we just needed a reason to fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我只想和你多分享几次胜利而已\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just wanted to share a few more victories with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那些不是胜利\N{\fnArial\fs48}Those weren't victories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等，石榴\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait, Garnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你看，我们相比你要弱小太多\N{\fnArial\fs48}You know, we're so much weaker than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}和你融合是我们感觉变强的一个\N{\fnArial\fs48}Fusing with you is like our one chance to feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}机会\N{\fnArial\fs48}Stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不要庇护她\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet: Don't defend her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橄榄石就在地球上某处，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot is out there somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而珍珠一直在分散我们的注意力...就因为些破事！\N{\fnArial\fs48}and Pearl's been distracting us with nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴...够了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet... That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶，跟我融合\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst, fuse with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但...\N{\fnArial\fs48}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}让我们赶紧结束这一切吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's just get this over with.
