Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.91,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}求求你原谅我吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Please forgive me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.94,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我当然会原谅你啦\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Of course I forgive you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我的天\N{\fnArial\fs48}Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}该有多好啊，\N{\fnArial\fs48}It sure would be nice
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果这能跟动画一样轻松解决\N{\fnArial\fs48}if things worked out the way they do in cartoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah.
